        Parameters:
        astarPosition - A* -algorithm with position based heuristic
        astarManhattan - A* -algorithm with manhattan heuristic
        astarLinear - A* -algorithm with manhattan + linear collision heuristic
        idaStarPosition - IDA* -algorithm with position based heuristic
        idaStarManhattan - IDA* -algorithm with manhattan heuristic
        idaStarLinear - IDA* -algorithm with manhattan + linear collision heuristic
        generator - Class for generating puzzles

        public long[] benchmark(ArrayList<Puzzle> puzzles,
